oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Cannon County Jail
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of the county jail and residence. Standing outside the home, from left to right, are Forrest Logan Stroud (1904-1983), Sheriff Beecher Burr Stroud (1875-1968), Etta Hoover Stroud (1874-1912), Rebecca E. Hoover McBroom (1855-1932), Birdie Stroud, Frances D Stroud Jaquith (1900-1969), Fannie McBroom Gilley (1851-1958), and Mayne Stroud.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
